title: Wild Card Previews!
itunes:title: Wild Card Previews!
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew starts up the show with what intrigues them in the AFC & NFC Wild Card match ups (0:30) and which coaching vacancies are the best jobs to take (7:04)? The gang then gets into the things they learned from Week 17 like people still doubting the Patriots (21:46) and how the future of the AFC North is Baker Mayfield vs Lamar Jackson (25:12). Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Kyle Brandt and Peter Schrager give their breakthrough players for the 2018 playoffs (35:43). Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!
